16 AN ACT TO REQUIRE MANDATORY RESTITUTION
17 TO BE AWARDED TO A VICTIM OF HUMAN
18 TRAFFICKING; AND TO AMEND THE ARKANSAS
19 CRIME VICTIMS REPARATIONS ACT.
